metadata.title: JC Polyomavirus transmission revealed by metagenomic virome sequencing in living donor-recipient kidney transplant pairs
metadata.description:
a) Viral reads and undetermined reads raw output files of VirMet bioinformatics pipeline

The files are named as follows: ID_D(onor)/R(ecipient)_weeks-after-transplantation_blood/urine_viral/undetermined-reads.fastq.gz

b) Consensus sequences of JC Polyomavirus isolates

The files are named as follows: ID_D(onor)/R(ecipient)_weeks-after-transplantation_blood/urine_reference-for-alignment_consensus.fasta

metadata.title: Metagenomic sequencing complements routine diagnostics in identifying viral pathogens in lung transplant recipients with unknown etiology of respiratory infection
metadata.description: Output of VirMet bioinformatic pipeline for all samples analysed. SAMPLE_viral_reads.fastq.gz files contain all recognised reads of viral origin, SAMPLE_undetermined_reads.fastq.gz reads of unknown origin.
